        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Bridge Investment Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires states to use at least 20% of certain FY2022-FY2025 federal highway funds to improve bridges, particularly those classified as being in poor condition.</p>]]>
        </text>
